WEBVTT

01:48.960 --> 01:51.160
Zhiyong, move that table over here.

01:51.360 --> 01:51.920
Align it to the right.

01:51.920 --> 01:52.450
This one.

01:52.479 --> 01:53.920
Yes.

01:56.840 --> 01:57.600
The pen fell.

02:05.400 --> 02:06.800
Yuanbao, let me help you.

02:07.360 --> 02:08.080
No need.

02:08.240 --> 02:09.080
I can do it myself.

02:09.080 --> 02:09.720
Yuanbao,

02:09.880 --> 02:11.560
didn't we agree to be sisters?

02:11.640 --> 02:13.080
You don't need to be so polite to me.

02:13.080 --> 02:14.280
Besides, as a girl,

02:14.280 --> 02:15.640
how can you carry such heavy water?

02:15.640 --> 02:16.500
Let me help you.

02:16.600 --> 02:17.400
No need.

02:17.680 --> 02:19.760
Really no need. I can do it.

02:20.040 --> 02:21.560
You still have a waist injury.

02:21.560 --> 02:22.920
You should be careful yourself.

02:22.920 --> 02:24.960
It's fine. My waist is much better now.

02:24.960 --> 02:26.960
Helping you carry water is no problem.

02:26.960 --> 02:27.560
It's okay.

02:27.640 --> 02:28.500
Really no need.

02:28.600 --> 02:29.400
Really.

02:33.120 --> 02:33.760
Xinrui.

02:37.000 --> 02:37.720
It's fine.

02:39.120 --> 02:40.040
Sorry, Xinrui.

02:40.079 --> 02:41.240
I didn't mean to.

02:41.440 --> 02:42.640
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

02:43.240 --> 02:44.400
She has a back injury.

02:44.400 --> 02:45.360
I know. I...

02:45.360 --> 02:46.880
Jingu, don't blame Yuanbao.

02:46.880 --> 02:47.920
It's all my fault.

02:48.160 --> 02:49.760
I insisted on helping her.

02:50.440 --> 02:52.100
She didn't push me on purpose.

02:52.360 --> 02:54.280
Yuanbao, I'm sorry.

02:54.760 --> 02:56.240
I just lost my balance.

02:56.720 --> 02:57.850
Please don't be mad.

03:00.760 --> 03:01.560
What's wrong?

03:03.360 --> 03:04.240
It's nothing.

03:05.000 --> 03:06.280
Don't make such a fuss.

03:06.760 --> 03:07.360
Yuanbao,

03:07.800 --> 03:09.800
I'm taking Xinrui to the infirmary.

03:09.800 --> 03:11.200
Okay, go ahead.

03:16.920 --> 03:19.040
I just gave her a push.

03:19.200 --> 03:20.920
Why did she fall?

03:40.600 --> 03:41.160
Ruirui.

03:42.120 --> 03:43.380
I'm here for class too.

03:43.960 --> 03:45.090
Why are you here too?

03:46.160 --> 03:47.960
I didn't do well on the last exam,

03:48.120 --> 03:49.450
so my mom dumped me here.

03:49.520 --> 03:50.800
She said she never wants to sit in

03:50.800 --> 03:52.760
that special seat for parents again.

03:52.760 --> 03:54.480
She said someone here can watch me do my homework,

03:54.480 --> 03:55.340
which is great.

03:56.640 --> 03:57.160
Ruirui,

03:58.000 --> 04:00.120
don't you think

04:00.360 --> 04:02.360
it's fate that brought us together?

04:03.480 --> 04:05.240
Stop being so cheesy.

04:11.680 --> 04:14.800
Does your mom hit you a lot?

04:15.400 --> 04:16.680
Not a lot.

04:17.160 --> 04:18.920
Only when I get bad grades

04:19.000 --> 04:20.200
or make her mad,

04:20.800 --> 04:22.730
she occasionally disciplines me.

04:25.360 --> 04:27.680
Even though you bicker with your mom,

04:28.040 --> 04:29.200
I always feel

04:29.480 --> 04:32.280
you two actually have a pretty good relationship.

04:33.400 --> 04:34.080
Yeah.

04:36.520 --> 04:38.040
My dad passed away early.

04:39.440 --> 04:41.240
My mom had to provide for the family

04:41.240 --> 04:42.920
and take care of me and my sister.

04:42.920 --> 04:44.520
It's really not easy for her.

04:45.960 --> 04:47.820
Also, these past couple of years,

04:48.440 --> 04:50.170
she hasn't been in good health.

04:51.320 --> 04:53.380
The doctor told her to exercise more.

04:54.480 --> 04:55.720
But my mom is so lazy.

04:56.159 --> 04:57.560
She doesn't want to move.

04:58.120 --> 04:59.480
So I have to use this method

04:59.480 --> 05:00.540
to force her to move

05:00.960 --> 05:01.880
and run more.

05:05.040 --> 05:06.640
You piss her off on purpose

05:07.320 --> 05:09.400
to make her chase you?

05:10.760 --> 05:12.600
That's how you help her.

05:13.720 --> 05:14.560
Smart, right?

05:17.200 --> 05:18.040
Aren't you afraid

05:18.040 --> 05:19.920
of giving her high blood pressure?

05:19.920 --> 05:20.920
No.

05:21.080 --> 05:22.000
My mom is the kind of person

05:22.000 --> 05:24.440
whose bark is worse than her bite when she's angry.

05:24.440 --> 05:26.160
She doesn't take things to heart.

05:26.160 --> 05:27.680
Even if she really gets angry,

05:27.680 --> 05:28.880
she'll be fine after beating me up.

05:28.880 --> 05:30.680
It's also a good workout for her.

05:30.880 --> 05:31.810
It's quite good.

05:33.000 --> 05:34.930
What kind of twisted logic is that?

05:37.040 --> 05:38.840
I'm not cut out for studying.

05:40.080 --> 05:42.210
And I don't have any special strengths

05:42.440 --> 05:43.960
for my mom to brag about.

05:45.480 --> 05:46.940
So I have to use this method

05:47.600 --> 05:48.600
to help her out.

05:49.880 --> 05:51.120
What's wrong?

05:52.200 --> 05:53.200
Did I scare you?

05:54.159 --> 05:55.000
No.

05:55.080 --> 05:56.880
Why aren't you saying anything?

05:58.840 --> 06:01.360
Actually, I understand you perfectly.

06:02.520 --> 06:03.880
My mom is quite busy.

06:04.680 --> 06:06.240
She has no time for me.

06:06.640 --> 06:09.100
My mom and I have been in a cold war for a while.

06:09.520 --> 06:11.720
I'm planning to go live at my grandma's.

06:12.520 --> 06:13.520
You can't do that.

06:14.920 --> 06:16.120
You two are mother and daughter.

06:16.120 --> 06:17.520
It should be easy to communicate.

06:17.520 --> 06:18.440
Just talk more.

06:19.120 --> 06:20.780
It's not easy being children,

06:21.360 --> 06:23.360
but it's even harder being parents.

06:24.160 --> 06:26.690
I didn't expect you to be so mature about this.

06:30.680 --> 06:31.320
Well.

06:32.040 --> 06:35.000
Tell you what. If you have any problems you don't know how to solve,

06:35.000 --> 06:36.760
just ask me. I'll teach you.

06:37.520 --> 06:38.560
Really?

06:41.600 --> 06:43.480
Okay, you said it.

06:44.040 --> 06:45.370
Don't find me annoying.

06:46.600 --> 06:48.040
Not annoying at all.

06:53.200 --> 06:55.000
Alright, everyone, quiet down.

06:55.000 --> 06:56.530
We are about to start class.

07:11.960 --> 07:13.320
Since we were young,

07:13.400 --> 07:16.080
your notes have always been neat and clean.

07:17.680 --> 07:20.200
Reading your notes is such a pleasure.

07:22.840 --> 07:24.520
The key points in this notebook

07:24.520 --> 07:26.050
are written in such detail.

07:26.360 --> 07:27.680
You always get a perfect score in physics.

07:27.680 --> 07:29.740
Do you still need to make these notes?

07:33.600 --> 07:35.120
You can do it, Yuanbao.

07:41.000 --> 07:43.960
I thought you made this especially for me.

07:44.400 --> 07:45.930
I'll make one for you later.

07:47.680 --> 07:50.159
Are you and Yuanbao close?

07:51.120 --> 07:53.650
We're desk-mates, so naturally we're close.

07:53.760 --> 07:55.290
We just help each other out.

07:55.840 --> 07:57.560
Closer than we are?

07:58.400 --> 07:59.330
It's different.

08:01.960 --> 08:04.090
Have you finished writing your notes?

08:04.560 --> 08:05.360
Done.

08:06.680 --> 08:08.480
Actually, I like Yuanbao too.

08:08.680 --> 08:10.280
I want to be friends with her.

08:10.840 --> 08:11.800
But I'm afraid

08:11.960 --> 08:13.720
that because of the water-carrying incident today,

08:13.720 --> 08:15.320
she won't come near me again.

08:15.800 --> 08:17.800
Why don't you help me, Jingu?

08:21.200 --> 08:22.200
What do you mean?

08:25.120 --> 08:25.880
Guess.

08:27.840 --> 08:28.640
Pass the ball.

08:31.080 --> 08:32.360
No one is defending him.

08:32.360 --> 08:33.200
Shoot.

08:33.799 --> 08:34.480
Missed.

08:35.400 --> 08:37.059
Class is over. Gather around.

08:45.280 --> 08:46.000
Mu Qingyun.

08:46.520 --> 08:47.320
What's wrong?

08:48.480 --> 08:49.880
The final exam is coming.

08:50.160 --> 08:52.920
During this time, I plan to spend half an hour every day after school

08:52.920 --> 08:54.320
tutoring Yuanbao.

08:54.800 --> 08:57.240
I will walk her home after tutoring.

08:57.680 --> 08:58.360
So,

08:58.760 --> 09:01.160
you don't need to wait for her after school.

09:07.520 --> 09:08.440
Stop it.

09:08.840 --> 09:09.400
Ruirui.

09:11.040 --> 09:11.800
Blockhead.

09:14.960 --> 09:15.890
What's going on?

09:43.720 --> 09:46.250
Later, based on your ability and foundation,

09:46.600 --> 09:48.000
I'll put together a set of

09:48.080 --> 09:49.610
physics summaries for you.

10:24.880 --> 10:25.480
Class,

10:26.120 --> 10:28.320
I have an announcement before we start.

10:28.320 --> 10:29.520
Gu Xinrui has a notebook

10:29.520 --> 10:30.720
that went missing in the classroom.

10:30.720 --> 10:31.640
Gu Xinrui,

10:31.880 --> 10:33.480
what kind of notebook was it?

10:33.920 --> 10:35.960
It was about this big,

10:36.160 --> 10:38.400
filled with physics notes.

10:38.760 --> 10:40.490
I put it on my desk this morning,

10:40.720 --> 10:42.920
but it was gone after PE class.

10:43.120 --> 10:44.080
Come on, class.

10:44.440 --> 10:47.000
Check your backpacks, drawers,

10:47.360 --> 10:48.240
and desks.

10:48.280 --> 10:49.540
Let's help her find it.

10:56.360 --> 10:57.520
That's the one.

11:09.840 --> 11:10.720
No.

11:11.400 --> 11:12.560
I don't know why

11:12.560 --> 11:14.220
this notebook is here with me.

11:15.320 --> 11:17.000
No, I mean,

11:17.080 --> 11:18.410
I really didn't take it.

11:19.280 --> 11:20.560
Yuanbao, it's okay.

11:21.160 --> 11:21.880
This notebook

11:21.880 --> 11:23.520
was organized by Meng Jingu

11:23.600 --> 11:24.520
to give to you.

11:24.760 --> 11:26.220
He just lent it to me first.

11:26.920 --> 11:29.200
Now that it's in your hands,

11:29.400 --> 11:30.600
let's just forget it.

11:31.320 --> 11:32.440
Sir, it's fine.

11:33.080 --> 11:33.520
Okay.

11:34.080 --> 11:34.800
No.

11:35.360 --> 11:36.240
I really don't know

11:36.240 --> 11:37.700
why this notebook is here.

11:38.440 --> 11:39.680
I really didn't take it.

11:39.680 --> 11:41.320
No one said you stole it.

11:41.600 --> 11:42.730
Don't be so anxious.

11:42.960 --> 11:44.620
It couldn't be Xiong Yuanbao.

11:46.280 --> 11:47.680
Why would she take your notebook?

11:47.680 --> 11:48.720
Exactly.

11:48.800 --> 11:50.880
If Yuanbao stole bread or sausages,

11:50.960 --> 11:52.080
I could understand.

11:52.080 --> 11:53.280
Stealing a notebook?

11:53.720 --> 11:54.560
Impossible.

11:54.720 --> 11:55.720
Definitely.

11:56.200 --> 11:57.600
What are you laughing at?

11:57.760 --> 11:59.890
Yuanbao doesn't know what's going on.

12:02.880 --> 12:05.080
I put the notebook in Yuanbao's drawer.

12:05.080 --> 12:06.240
Weren't you nagging this morning

12:06.240 --> 12:08.920
that you needed to give this notebook to Yuanbao?

12:08.920 --> 12:09.760
Yuanbao wasn't here,

12:09.760 --> 12:11.490
so you asked me to give it to her.

12:13.680 --> 12:15.120
I forgot.

12:15.480 --> 12:16.520
Sorry, Yuanbao.

12:16.800 --> 12:17.840
I told you.

12:17.960 --> 12:20.040
I can understand Yuanbao stealing food.

12:20.040 --> 12:21.000
Stealing a notebook?

12:21.000 --> 12:21.920
You're kidding.

12:21.920 --> 12:23.080
Of course.

12:23.280 --> 12:23.880
All right.

12:24.000 --> 12:25.320
Since it's a misunderstanding, it's fine.

12:25.320 --> 12:26.480
Go back to your seats.

12:26.480 --> 12:27.200
Take out your test papers.

12:27.200 --> 12:29.730
We'll continue to go over yesterday's paper.

12:34.360 --> 12:35.240
Villain.

12:39.720 --> 12:42.120
So the answer to question 4 is A.

12:42.440 --> 12:43.480
Do you all get it?

12:43.600 --> 12:44.360
Question 4.

12:44.560 --> 12:45.240
Got it.

12:46.400 --> 12:48.560
Now let's do the next question.

12:55.320 --> 12:56.760
Final exams are coming up soon.

12:56.760 --> 12:58.880
Every day after school during this period,

12:58.880 --> 13:00.940
how about I tutor you for half an hour?

13:02.920 --> 13:04.520
No need to trouble yourself.

13:04.600 --> 13:07.000
I can study by myself when I go home at night.

13:07.040 --> 13:08.840
Thanks, deskmate.

13:20.560 --> 13:23.220
You finally remembered to treat me to ice cream.

13:23.760 --> 13:25.220
I've kept them all in mind.

13:25.280 --> 13:27.080
I was just saving them up for you.

13:27.320 --> 13:29.050
At least you have a conscience.

13:31.040 --> 13:31.760
Blockhead.

13:32.960 --> 13:34.090
Thank you for today.

13:34.520 --> 13:35.720
Why are you thanking me all of a sudden?

13:35.720 --> 13:38.040
I mean about the notebook today.

13:38.280 --> 13:40.600
I know you didn't put it in my drawer.

13:41.680 --> 13:42.680
How do you know?

13:43.520 --> 13:44.760
If it were really you,

13:45.240 --> 13:46.880
with Gu Xinrui looking for it for so long,

13:46.880 --> 13:48.610
you would have said it long ago.

13:49.560 --> 13:50.920
Waiting until everyone suspected me

13:50.920 --> 13:51.920
to stand up for me,

13:52.320 --> 13:54.850
I know you were trying to get me out of trouble.

13:56.040 --> 13:57.400
You've grown a brain.

14:00.680 --> 14:02.340
Didn't you suspect I stole it?

14:04.120 --> 14:06.440
With your brain, stealing?

14:07.320 --> 14:08.720
If you could steal things,

14:08.720 --> 14:10.640
then I could buy a house on Mars.

14:12.720 --> 14:14.400
You believe in me that much?

14:18.240 --> 14:20.170
Even if the whole world doubts you,

14:20.200 --> 14:21.600
I wouldn't suspect you.

14:26.800 --> 14:27.530
How was that?

14:27.600 --> 14:28.680
It's a new line I learned.

14:28.680 --> 14:30.410
Did it sound cool when I said it?

14:33.080 --> 14:35.640
By the way, when is your dad coming back?

14:35.880 --> 14:36.600
My dad?

14:37.600 --> 14:38.800
I called him.

14:38.840 --> 14:41.100
He said he inspected the area for a while,

14:41.120 --> 14:41.840
and it's not bad,

14:41.840 --> 14:43.170
so he's staying to work.

14:44.120 --> 14:45.650
What about you and your mom?

14:45.880 --> 14:48.280
Of course my mom and I are staying.

14:51.680 --> 14:53.240
Why are you looking like that?

14:53.240 --> 14:54.570
Trying to drive us away?

14:54.840 --> 14:55.880
Not exactly.

14:58.920 --> 14:59.650
Don't worry.

14:59.960 --> 15:01.490
Even if we really have to go,

15:02.040 --> 15:04.080
we won't abandon you and Grandma.

15:05.080 --> 15:07.120
If we leave, we leave together.

15:07.760 --> 15:08.960
We are a family.

15:22.560 --> 15:24.600
Ever since the notebook incident,

15:25.080 --> 15:26.400
I don't know why,

15:26.480 --> 15:27.480
I've been deliberately

15:27.480 --> 15:29.560
keeping my distance from Meng Jingu.

15:30.560 --> 15:32.160
With the first year of high school ending

15:32.160 --> 15:33.920
and class division coming up in the second year,

15:33.920 --> 15:36.650
I wanted to devote myself entirely to my studies.

15:36.960 --> 15:38.440
However, more often than not,

15:38.440 --> 15:41.120
things don't go as we expect.

15:42.000 --> 15:43.400
Surprises and accidents

15:43.400 --> 15:44.930
always come unexpectedly.

15:45.600 --> 15:47.080
Freshman year is almost over.

15:47.080 --> 15:48.340
I got you a little gift.

15:50.040 --> 15:50.960
For me?

15:51.760 --> 15:52.440
Of course.

15:54.040 --> 15:54.720
Take it.

15:55.600 --> 15:57.130
I picked it out just for you.

15:57.400 --> 15:58.480
I hope you like it.

15:58.880 --> 15:59.640
What is it?

15:59.880 --> 16:00.760
Open it and see.

16:05.640 --> 16:06.280
A puzzle.

16:08.120 --> 16:08.720
All right.

16:09.000 --> 16:10.400
I'll do it with Ruirui,

16:10.600 --> 16:11.720
so it'll be faster.

16:11.760 --> 16:12.400
No.

16:15.720 --> 16:16.720
My secret is written

16:16.720 --> 16:17.920
on the back.

16:18.600 --> 16:19.640
Besides you,

16:20.000 --> 16:21.160
no one else can know.

16:22.800 --> 16:25.480
Okay then, I'll do it secretly by myself

16:25.720 --> 16:26.850
and not tell anyone.

16:29.600 --> 16:30.280
Yuanbao.

16:32.640 --> 16:33.600
Are you still mad at me

16:33.600 --> 16:35.200
about the notebook incident

16:35.240 --> 16:36.120
last time?

16:38.240 --> 16:39.880
Why would I be mad at you?

16:40.080 --> 16:41.760
Xinrui grabbed it from me,

16:41.960 --> 16:44.360
saying she wanted to give it to you herself.

16:45.480 --> 16:48.120
Mutou already explained this to me.

16:48.760 --> 16:49.690
It's in the past.

16:59.560 --> 17:01.090
You have grass on your head.

17:07.520 --> 17:08.119
Let's go.

17:53.880 --> 17:56.840
Did you make up with your desk mate again?

17:58.120 --> 17:59.520
What do you mean made up?

17:59.560 --> 18:00.520
Don't talk nonsense.

18:00.520 --> 18:02.320
We've always been on good terms.

18:04.000 --> 18:06.480
What's in such a big box?

18:07.600 --> 18:08.240
A puzzle.

18:10.040 --> 18:10.970
How unoriginal.

18:12.480 --> 18:13.880
As if yours are creative.

18:14.080 --> 18:17.040
You either give caterpillars or dead mice.

18:50.560 --> 18:52.160
This should be the last time

18:52.160 --> 18:54.020
writing Class 20, Grade 1, right?

19:40.920 --> 19:41.760
Hello, Mr. Liu.

19:41.760 --> 19:42.620
Hello, Mr. Liu.

19:46.120 --> 19:47.080
Mr. Liu Li.

19:49.520 --> 19:50.240
Ms. Xu.

19:50.600 --> 19:51.440
Well,

19:51.520 --> 19:53.560
isn't this semester ending soon?

19:53.720 --> 19:55.980
Time flies, and it's hard to say goodbye.

19:56.360 --> 19:57.840
Thank you for taking care of me.

19:57.840 --> 20:00.770
So I brought some local specialties from my hometown

20:01.000 --> 20:01.680
for you.

20:03.080 --> 20:04.280
I'm so thrilled.

20:05.520 --> 20:06.040
Listen,

20:06.240 --> 20:08.300
call me anytime if you need anything.

20:08.320 --> 20:10.360
I'll be there for you right away.

20:10.600 --> 20:12.720
Please continue to look after me next semester.

20:12.720 --> 20:13.520
Okay.

20:13.720 --> 20:15.080
See you next semester then.

20:15.080 --> 20:16.320
Okay, no problem.

20:16.520 --> 20:17.040
Bye.

20:17.280 --> 20:19.280
You can call me during the holidays.

20:19.480 --> 20:20.600
My phone is on 24/7.

20:20.680 --> 20:21.280
Okay.

20:25.320 --> 20:26.000
Tian Yong.

20:28.360 --> 20:30.360
The eggs Ms. Xu gave me.

20:31.640 --> 20:32.570
Are you jealous?

20:34.440 --> 20:35.560
We all have them.

20:35.720 --> 20:38.280
Two boxes.

20:44.680 --> 20:45.640
I have some too.

20:54.680 --> 20:55.410
Did you know?

20:56.200 --> 20:58.760
Tong Ruirui and her mom went on a trip.

21:00.120 --> 21:01.080
Xing Yaqi is going to Beijing next month

21:01.080 --> 21:02.440
for a summer camp.

21:03.400 --> 21:05.560
Gao Jingyi is visiting her relatives.

21:07.200 --> 21:08.800
During this wonderful time,

21:09.000 --> 21:11.120
we're stuck at home doing homework.

21:13.480 --> 21:15.600
Life is so unfair.

21:16.080 --> 21:17.880
What? You want to go out and play?

21:18.440 --> 21:19.200
Don't you?

21:20.640 --> 21:22.300
Last time we went to Shanghai,

21:22.400 --> 21:24.330
we didn't have time to look around.

21:24.520 --> 21:26.450
I wonder when we'll go there again.

21:27.680 --> 21:30.800
What if we apply to a university

21:31.360 --> 21:32.880
in Shanghai in the future?

21:34.720 --> 21:37.180
I still want to go to a university in Beijing.

21:37.720 --> 21:40.520
Don't limit yourself.

21:41.240 --> 21:42.960
A real man should have high ambitions

21:42.960 --> 21:44.360
and let his talents soar.

21:47.000 --> 21:48.000
Fly where?

21:49.280 --> 21:51.410
With your grades, where can you fly to?

21:51.480 --> 21:53.880
Summer vacation is the best time to review.

21:54.400 --> 21:56.060
Ask Yuanbao if you don't know.

21:57.120 --> 21:58.960
Your midterm exams were fine,

21:59.040 --> 22:00.640
but how many places did you drop in the final exam?

22:00.640 --> 22:02.680
Don't even think about going anywhere this summer.

22:02.680 --> 22:04.610
Stay home and review your lessons.

22:04.920 --> 22:05.840
Mom. Auntie.

22:06.160 --> 22:07.160
Don't call me mom.

22:08.280 --> 22:09.000
Study.

22:14.760 --> 22:16.120
My mom's been nagging about my grades

22:16.120 --> 22:17.560
for half the vacation.

22:17.800 --> 22:19.640
I'm telling you, my mom's nagging skills

22:19.640 --> 22:21.970
aren't something just anyone can master.

22:27.920 --> 22:29.600
Look at Meng Jingu's notes.

22:29.880 --> 22:31.410
Don't let them mislead you.

22:32.960 --> 22:34.000
What do you know?

22:34.200 --> 22:35.080
With this,

22:35.320 --> 22:37.440
it's like having a secret martial arts manual.

22:37.440 --> 22:38.880
It gets twice the result with half the effort.

22:38.880 --> 22:40.680
It's the essence of the essence.

22:42.040 --> 22:44.440
I think my mom is really right.

22:45.480 --> 22:47.480
Your grades shouldn't have dropped.

22:47.480 --> 22:49.480
Why did they drop?

22:49.640 --> 22:51.560
Don't you know?

22:51.800 --> 22:55.130
That's because the questions this time were too hard, okay?

22:56.920 --> 22:58.650
I'm not talking to you anymore.

22:58.840 --> 22:59.840
My stomach hurts.

23:04.400 --> 23:07.480
Grandma, my stomach hurts.

23:08.120 --> 23:09.280
Go quickly, go.

23:09.480 --> 23:11.410
I'll find you some medicine later.

23:24.720 --> 23:26.840
This kid really has a way.

23:28.800 --> 23:30.880
What new trick is in this gift box?

23:37.520 --> 23:38.250
What is this?

23:40.880 --> 23:41.720
A puzzle.

23:44.320 --> 23:45.280
With words on it.

23:46.160 --> 23:48.820
This kid really has a lot of tricks up his sleeve.

23:49.280 --> 23:52.010
Yuanbao's grades dropped so much because of him.

23:52.040 --> 23:54.570
And now he's distracting her with this stuff.

24:00.440 --> 24:01.360
This guy.

24:02.440 --> 24:04.880
Meng Jingu, you really have some tricks.

24:05.000 --> 24:06.730
Who could possibly solve this?

24:13.520 --> 24:14.400
Clever kid.

24:23.880 --> 24:25.880
I knew there was a message.

24:27.080 --> 24:28.400
Are you...

24:29.160 --> 24:30.560
using secret codes, kid?

24:31.160 --> 24:32.360
What is this?

24:32.800 --> 24:35.120
Would you my Zi be...

24:35.360 --> 24:37.120
Would you

24:38.760 --> 24:39.880
be my...

24:43.680 --> 24:45.800
Would you be my Zixia?

24:49.080 --> 24:50.810
You little rascal, Meng Jingu.

24:51.160 --> 24:52.440
Impossible.

24:55.040 --> 24:55.560
Keep

24:55.800 --> 24:57.260
dreaming. In your dreams!

25:00.720 --> 25:01.960
Why are there so many?

25:02.080 --> 25:03.480
How can I tell them apart?

25:06.920 --> 25:07.920
Yuanbao.

25:08.800 --> 25:09.680
Grandma.

25:13.680 --> 25:15.240
You got a lot today.

25:20.320 --> 25:22.200
You eat so little every night.

25:22.320 --> 25:23.840
I don't dare to cook too much.

25:23.840 --> 25:24.700
Are you hungry?

25:24.800 --> 25:26.280
I'll go get you something to eat.

25:26.280 --> 25:27.400
It's okay, Grandma.

25:27.400 --> 25:28.960
I'm not hungry. Make less.

25:29.600 --> 25:30.800
I heard

25:31.200 --> 25:33.200
eating too much will make me stupid.

25:33.280 --> 25:34.840
Okay, I'll listen to you.

25:37.920 --> 25:40.880
Isn't it a bit immoral not to let her see it?

25:57.480 --> 25:59.400
Grandma, where is Yuanbao?

25:59.920 --> 26:02.180
He has a stomachache. He's in the toilet.

26:03.000 --> 26:05.080
I left something behind. I'll go get it.

26:05.080 --> 26:06.160
Okay, go ahead.

26:51.520 --> 26:54.120
It's so much, it will take me forever to finish.

26:54.800 --> 26:58.200
I still want to take some extra classes this summer vacation.

27:00.000 --> 27:01.060
Morning, Grandma.

27:01.840 --> 27:03.960
It's summer vacation, I want you to sleep more,

27:03.960 --> 27:05.220
so I didn't wake you up.

27:05.640 --> 27:07.080
Breakfast is on the table.

27:07.080 --> 27:08.000
Go eat.

27:11.520 --> 27:13.200
Mutou, why are you so early?

27:16.040 --> 27:17.920
What's wrong? Do you have a cold?

27:17.920 --> 27:19.080
Yeah.

27:19.080 --> 27:19.960
Didn't you say that this summer,

27:19.960 --> 27:21.440
you wanted to catch up on your studies?

27:21.440 --> 27:22.480
So I asked Xing Yaqi

27:22.480 --> 27:24.120
for her notebook and made a copy.

27:24.120 --> 27:26.520
It's definitely better than Meng Jingu's.

27:26.560 --> 27:27.280
Take a look.

27:29.560 --> 27:30.160
My god.

27:30.440 --> 27:32.840
This is exactly what I've been dreaming of.

27:34.840 --> 27:37.080
Our class monitor never disappoints.

27:37.440 --> 27:38.760
It's so detailed.

27:39.200 --> 27:42.680
It's just that someone's handwriting is a bit ugly.

27:44.800 --> 27:46.640
Mutou, you are so good to me.

27:47.480 --> 27:48.080
Tell me,

27:48.520 --> 27:50.960
how do you want me to reward you?

27:52.080 --> 27:52.920
Up to you.

27:53.640 --> 27:54.500
I'm going back.

28:00.280 --> 28:00.920
Mutou.

28:12.280 --> 28:13.640
Why does he have a fever?

28:14.160 --> 28:16.360
I don't know what he was tinkering with last night.

28:16.360 --> 28:17.560
He was at it all night.

28:17.600 --> 28:19.680
I saw him writing something when I got up to use the bathroom.

28:19.680 --> 28:20.740
I just ignored him.

28:20.840 --> 28:22.560
And he had a fever this morning.

28:22.560 --> 28:24.040
I've told him so many times

28:24.120 --> 28:25.000
not to stay up late,

28:25.000 --> 28:26.280
but he just wouldn't listen.

28:26.280 --> 28:27.080
Now he's sick.

28:27.280 --> 28:28.160
It's okay.

28:28.440 --> 28:30.370
I just wiped him down with alcohol.

28:30.520 --> 28:32.240
He also took some fever medicine.

28:32.240 --> 28:34.840
He just needs to sweat it out under the blanket.

28:36.280 --> 28:38.810
Is the ginger soup still boiling on the stove?

28:39.720 --> 28:41.280
Look at my memory.

28:42.040 --> 28:43.700
I forgot to turn off the stove.

28:46.520 --> 28:47.920
I'll go change his water.

28:48.040 --> 28:49.120
Call me if you need anything.

28:49.120 --> 28:49.680
Okay.

29:02.120 --> 29:03.120
Now you're sick.

29:04.120 --> 29:05.720
You're usually so bossy,

29:05.800 --> 29:07.130
and always bullying me.

29:13.800 --> 29:15.330
Why is he burning up so much?

29:15.800 --> 29:16.480
No.

29:17.080 --> 29:18.680
I have to go buy a fever patch.

29:50.320 --> 29:51.380
What are you doing?

29:52.200 --> 29:53.960
You almost crushed me to death.

29:55.720 --> 29:57.320
When have I ever bullied you?

29:59.200 --> 30:00.640
Weren't you asleep?

30:04.520 --> 30:06.200
You guys woke me up.

30:07.760 --> 30:09.090
How are you feeling now?

30:09.600 --> 30:11.260
Has your fever gone down a bit?

30:14.600 --> 30:15.400
Don't move.

30:15.560 --> 30:17.640
You need to rest more when you're sick.

30:17.640 --> 30:18.760
Well, I...

30:19.600 --> 30:21.120
What do you mean 'I'?

30:21.400 --> 30:23.260
You're usually as strong as an ox.

30:23.560 --> 30:25.290
How come you're so fragile now?

30:25.680 --> 30:26.440
I think

30:26.520 --> 30:28.440
I should just call you Lin Meimei from now on.

30:28.440 --> 30:29.960
Catching a breeze and staying up late,

30:29.960 --> 30:31.520
and you get a fever like this.

30:31.520 --> 30:33.120
If your fever continues like this,

30:33.120 --> 30:34.580
you're going to be cooked.

30:35.080 --> 30:36.000
I... no.

30:36.120 --> 30:36.680
No.

30:37.600 --> 30:39.120
Stop being stubborn.

30:39.320 --> 30:40.200
Listen to me.

30:40.520 --> 30:42.650
You need to keep warm when you're sick.

30:42.880 --> 30:45.360
Sweat it out and stay under the covers.

30:45.680 --> 30:48.210
Just lie down and tell me if you need anything.

30:48.440 --> 30:50.760
Really? Then I'll say it.

30:52.360 --> 30:54.120
If I don't go now,

30:54.640 --> 30:55.970
I'm going to wet the bed.

30:59.680 --> 31:01.440
Then go. Go.

31:08.000 --> 31:08.600
I,

31:08.960 --> 31:09.720
well...

31:10.440 --> 31:11.160
Yuanbao.

31:11.880 --> 31:14.640
Don't worry about me. I'm fine.

31:15.040 --> 31:16.240
Well, you...

31:17.760 --> 31:18.960
What's wrong with me?

31:19.400 --> 31:20.440
She should see the message

31:20.440 --> 31:22.680
behind the puzzle in a while.

31:29.720 --> 31:31.320
To copy notes for me,

31:31.480 --> 31:32.960
he didn't sleep all night

31:33.120 --> 31:34.720
and made himself sick.

31:35.400 --> 31:36.720
What a silly blockhead.
